sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant DB as Dashboard
    participant Collections as Collections
    participant Scenarios as Scenarios
    participant Backend as Backend
    participant AI as Groq API
    participant Supabase as Supabase

    User->>DB: 1. Opens Dashboard
    DB->>Supabase: Fetch user data
    Supabase-->>DB: Return stats & readiness
    DB-->>User: Display analytics

    User->>Collections: 2. Browse Collections
    Collections->>Backend: Request topics
    Backend->>Supabase: Get collections
    Supabase-->>Backend: Return data
    Backend-->>Collections: Display topics

    User->>Collections: 3. Select Learning Path

    alt Collections - Mock Interview
        User->>Collections: Select topic & difficulty
        Collections->>AI: Generate interview questions
        AI-->>Collections: Return questions
        User->>Collections: Answer questions
        Collections->>AI: Evaluate responses
        AI-->>Collections: Return feedback & score
        Collections-->>User: Display interview results
    else Collections - Problems/Learning
        User->>Collections: Learn Subject
        Collections->>Supabase: Fetch Content
        Supabase-->>Collections: Return Content
        User->>Collections: View problem
        User->>Collections: Submit solution
        Collections->>Backend: Validate answer
        Backend-->>Collections: Correct/Incorrect result
        Collections-->>User: Display result & points
    else Daily Challenges
        User->>Collections: View daily challenge
        Collections->>Backend: Get challenge of the day
        Backend->>Supabase: Fetch challenge
        Supabase-->>Backend: Return challenge
        Backend-->>Collections: Display challenge
        User->>Collections: Solve challenge
        Collections->>Backend: Validate solution
        Backend-->>Collections: Award points/streak
        Collections-->>User: Display reward
    else Scenario Practice Path
        User->>Scenarios: Select scenario
        Scenarios->>Backend: Request module
        Backend->>Supabase: Get scenario content
        Supabase-->>Backend: Return content
        Backend-->>Scenarios: Display module
        User->>Scenarios: View explanation & video
        User->>Scenarios: Complete quiz
        User->>Scenarios: Take mock interview
        Scenarios->>AI: Send answers
        AI-->>Scenarios: Return feedback
        Scenarios-->>User: Display performance
    end

    Collections->>Backend: 4. Update progress
    Scenarios->>Backend: Update progress
    Backend->>Supabase: Save: streak +1, badges, XP
    Supabase-->>Backend: Confirmed
    Backend-->>Collections: Show rewards earned
    Backend-->>Scenarios: Show rewards earned
    Collections-->>User: Display rewards
    Scenarios-->>User: Display rewards

    alt View Profile
        User->>DB: 5. View updated profile
        DB->>Supabase: Refresh stats
        Supabase-->>DB: Return updated data
        DB-->>User: Display readiness & leaderboard
    else View Leaderboard
        User->>DB: Check leaderboard
        DB->>Supabase: Fetch global rankings
        Supabase-->>DB: Return leaderboard data
        DB-->>User: Display leaderboard & rankings
    end

